291
00:39:50,913 --> 00:39:55,515
Drone broj tri,
ti ces da rukovodis kiseonickom anestezijom.

292
00:40:04,144 --> 00:40:06,443
Drone broj jedan.

293
00:40:11,429 --> 00:40:15,169
Broj jedan, ti ces da asistiras.

294
00:41:31,869 --> 00:41:34,744
Komandire Anderson.

295
00:41:34,935 --> 00:41:38,291
Ne mogu ni blizu da pridjem
tom glavnom bus kanalu.

296
00:41:38,483 --> 00:41:41,168
Sve je tako pokidano ovde.

297
00:41:43,085 --> 00:41:45,866
Slusaj, Freeman.
To ti je ime, jel' tako?

298
00:41:46,057 --> 00:41:47,591
Da.

299
00:41:47,688 --> 00:41:50,085
- Imas porodicu, Freeman?
- Ne, sir.

300
00:41:51,234 --> 00:41:53,248
Dobro, slusaj, Freeman.

301
00:41:53,343 --> 00:41:57,562
Bio si uz ovaj projekat od
samog starta, i znao si za rizike.

302
00:41:57,754 --> 00:41:58,712
Da, sir.

303
00:41:58,904 --> 00:42:03,409
Stvarno ne znam
kako da ovo kazem, Freeman.

304
00:42:04,945 --> 00:42:06,765
U redu je, sir.

305
00:42:06,861 --> 00:42:10,408
- Imamo problema.
- Shvatio sam.

306
00:42:10,505 --> 00:42:12,517
Da.

307
00:42:13,860 --> 00:42:17,984
- Stvarno mi je zao, Freeman.
- Zao, sir? Zbog cega?

308
00:42:18,077 --> 00:42:22,106
Necemo te moci zaustaviti
pre nego sto udaris u prstenove.

309
00:42:23,162 --> 00:42:25,270
Vidim.

310
00:42:25,365 --> 00:42:28,433
Freeman, mogao bi da uzmes u obzir...

311
