Drone broj tri, nastavi da se kreces.

324
00:45:18,892 --> 00:45:20,811
Prati jedinicu i dvojku.

325
00:45:23,784 --> 00:45:25,797
Prati jedan i dva!

326
00:45:32,988 --> 00:45:34,906
Zasto ih nisi pratio?

327
00:48:25,462 --> 00:48:27,572
A sad mu iskopajte rupu.

328
00:48:27,667 --> 00:48:32,270
Neka bude sedam stopa dugacka...
i tri stope siroka.

329
00:49:00,168 --> 00:49:03,428
OK, Sad ga ubacite...
spustite ga unutra.

330
00:49:11,289 --> 00:49:15,700
A onda ostanite tu,
zato sto hocu nesto da kazem...

331
00:49:15,797 --> 00:49:18,192
