332
00:49:28,356 --> 00:49:32,287
Voleo bih da mogu da kazem molitvu...

333
00:49:36,888 --> 00:49:38,806
..ali ne znam...

334
00:49:39,956 --> 00:49:42,544
..zapravo kako to da kazem.

335
00:49:45,037 --> 00:49:48,872
Wolf i Barker i Keenan,...

336
00:49:51,270 --> 00:49:54,434
..nisu bas bili moji prijatelji.

337
00:49:56,639 --> 00:49:58,557
Ali sam ih voleo.

338
00:50:01,817 --> 00:50:03,733
I...

339
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:15,716
..Ne znam... Ne znam da li...

340
00:50:17,059 --> 00:50:19,456
..cu ikada biti u stanju...

341
00:50:21,853 --> 00:50:24,633
..da se opravdam za ono sto sam uradio,...

342
